definitions.definition: Any female celebrity , usually a well known singer or actress.
A person with an inflated sense of self , who has high expectations of others, and who is extremely demanding and fussy when it comes to personal privileges .
A person who slays in a confident and feminine manner.

main_definition: Any female celebrity , usually a well known singer or actress. [from the 19th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( slang , derogatory , informal ) A person with an inflated sense of self , who has high expectations of others, and who is extremely demanding and fussy when it comes to personal privileges .
( Internet slang ) A person who slays in a confident and feminine manner.
